des: EchoVibe FM, established by the Yoruba Heritage Association in Dallas, Texas, is dedicated to celebrating and promoting the rich cultural tapestry of Nigeria and beyond through an online radio platform. Our mission is to provide a platform for cultural expression, education, and entertainment, connecting diverse communities through a wide range of music genres and engaging content. Our slogan, "In Tune with Your Roots," reflects our commitment to embracing and showcasing cultural heritage.
